    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given that ASTM F1717 specifies a single standardized configuration and all three QoIs satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds across N=11 constructs at two independent laboratories. Overall simulation credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory decision.",
